instanceFields.label: Count
instanceFields.description: The number of elements in the list.

instanceMethods.label: Get
instanceMethods.description: Get the element at the specified index.

parameters.name: index
parameters.description: The index of the element to get (negative indices count from the end).

instanceMethods.label: Set
instanceMethods.description: Set the element at the specified index.

parameters.name: index
parameters.description: The index of the element to set (negative indices count from the end).

instanceMethods.label: Add
instanceMethods.description: Add an element to the end of the list.

instanceMethods.label: InsertAt
instanceMethods.description: Insert an element at the specified index.

parameters.name: index
parameters.description: The index at which to insert (negative indices count from the end).

instanceMethods.label: RemoveAt
instanceMethods.description: Remove the element at the specified index.

parameters.name: index
parameters.description: The index of the element to remove (negative indices count from the end).

instanceMethods.label: Remove
instanceMethods.description: Remove the first occurrence of the specified element.

instanceMethods.label: Contains
instanceMethods.description: Check if the list contains the specified element.

instanceMethods.label: SortCustom
instanceMethods.description: Sort the list using a custom method, expects a method with the signature int method(a,b).

parameters.name: method
parameters.description: The comparison method that returns an int: negative if a < b, 0 if a == b, positive if a > b.

instanceMethods.label: Filter
instanceMethods.description: Filter the list using a custom method, expects a method with the signature bool method(element).

parameters.name: method
parameters.description: The predicate method that returns true for elements to keep.

instanceMethods.label: Map
instanceMethods.description: Map the list using a custom method, expects a method with the signature object method(element).

parameters.name: method
parameters.description: The transformation method that returns the mapped value for each element.

instanceMethods.label: Reduce
instanceMethods.description: Reduce the list using a custom method, expects a method with the signature object method(acc, element).

parameters.name: method
parameters.description: The accumulation method that combines the accumulator with each element.

instanceMethods.label: Randomize
instanceMethods.description: Returns a randomized version of the list.

instanceMethods.label: ToSet
instanceMethods.description: Convert the list to a set.

parameters.name: parameterValues
parameters.description: The values to add to the list.

constructors.description: Creates a list with the specified values.
